  congr, funext e i o k k', exact propext
    ⟨λ ⟨⟨h, ei, eo⟩, ee⟩, ⟨⟨h, ee⟩, ei, eo⟩,
     λ ⟨⟨h, ee⟩, ei, eo⟩,  ⟨⟨h, ei, eo⟩, ee⟩⟩
